            <title>[LU-15469] Automate Lustre Upgrade/Downgrade Testing</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15469</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As part of the Lustre release testing, we run upgrade and downgrade of Lustre from/to the last LTS version and, if different from LTS, the last release. We run this for ldiskfs and for ZFS and we for rolling, one server type then clients at a time, and clean, all at once, upgrade/downgrade. &lt;/p&gt;

